{"word":"βελτίων","slug":"βελτίων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βελτίων</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>attic <a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> of <a href='S:ἀγαθός'><el>ἀγαθός</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:confer, compare'>Cf.</a> <a href='S:βέλτερος'><el>βέλτερος</el></a>\n<p/><i>better</i>, <el>ἐπὶ τὸ βέλτιον χωρεῖν</el> <i>to improve, advance</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/>"}]}